My dear Brother

.fo +
Thanks for the note from Brother Gundert. I have nothing to send but love.
Mrs West sends a note and a bottle of Mango jelly for Mrs Gundert. I have
just heard from General West my dear Father who says that Mrs West is in a
dying state. So I trust that you will pray for her that she may depart in
the Lord. Amen. We are all well by the Lord ...
